Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Wednesday! Sorry this one=E2=80=99s a little delayed =E2=80=93 I got =
knocked out by a cold last week, and writing fiction is much harder than I =
thought!
Fiction? Things have been moving very fast recently, and while serious anal=
ysis [ https://substack.com/redirect/7f82ec6c-5e5d-4c61-80bf-a3ba8f10cd91?j=
=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] can be =
useful, fiction can be an equally potent way to explore where all of this i=
s heading. I mentioned before [ https://substack.com/redirect/17af3ab4-34a3=
-47d5-b9dc-21d3cc6425e0?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbq=
Osa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] that I wanted to start writing some short sci-fi about ou=
r portfolio companies, but I don=E2=80=99t want them to be the victims of m=
y poor first attempts, so I=E2=80=99m going with a less specific one today.=
=C2=A0
This first foray is about something a lot of people are very worried about =
but that I=E2=80=99m pretty excited by: humans=E2=80=99 place in the world =
in the face of AI=E2=80=99s growing capabilities.
It=E2=80=99s about something that humans are still best at, and that I thin=
k we=E2=80=99ll remain best at for a long time: generating fresh ideas, the=
 genesis sparks that set the machines in motion.=20
I=E2=80=99m not sure exactly how the idea for this particular story came ab=
out =E2=80=93 identifying all of the inspirations is as difficult as untang=
ling the images that go into a Stable Diffusion output or the sources that =
feed ChatGPT=E2=80=99s responses =E2=80=93 but I know a few of the things t=
hat bounced around in my brain, collided, and turned into this story. It=E2=
=80=99s a continuation of The Enchanted Notebook [ https://substack.com/red=
irect/04f032f1-bb1e-4aa3-8fb6-40056c830f0c?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7Gn=
A_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], which I wrote back in September, befo=
re things got really weird; plays off of John Palmer=E2=80=99s Idea Guy [ h=
ttps://substack.com/redirect/8d7b5f08-3264-4860-8af0-faa7c16626d7?j=3DeyJ1I=
joiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] meme; it=E2=80=
=99s inspired by Asimov=E2=80=99s The Last Question [ https://substack.com/=
redirect/cb4d3b30-c02c-4abc-a815-04b5c642787f?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T=
