 style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 2=
0px 0;"><span>Even in 1996, a car would have been the superior choice for t=
raversing 26.2 miles, and a boat would have effortlessly outpaced any human=
 swimmer across 400 meters. The hunt for sustenance, assuming grocery store=
s were absent, would have been better served by a shotgun rather than a jav=
elin. Geep offered Maya cap after cap of ancient contests, yet she failed t=
o find a single one with practical value. </span><em>Bump</em><span>.&#160;=
</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; =
margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Humans had earned these skills from evolutionary=
 necessity, and they were no longer very necessary, but they persisted in o=
ur bodies. And so, every four years, the world gathered to celebrate those =
who retained these abilities best. They did it because it was fun, because =
it gave them something to root for and strive towards, and because they cou=
ld. </span><em>Bop</em><span>.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; =
font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>The pinball =
that was the idea ricocheted around her brain, picking up wisps and tidbits=
, picking up momentum. Over her thirty-six years, so many intellectual skil=
ls joined physical ones in going the way of the pole vault. </span><em>Pop<=
/em><span>.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; li=
ne-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">If she had been born a generation ear=
lier, as a half-Indian, her parents would have nudged her into a career as =
a doctor, a lawyer, or an engineer. Close call.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color:=
 #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">After 20=
29&#8217;s landmark Garcia v. Kaiser Permanente San Diego Medical Center ca=
